                        <interp inst="t18391125-260-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 16.—Of stealing the watch.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy</hi>.—
